Package: getsat
Title: Retrieving Commonly Used Satellite Data
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2025-03-21
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Maintainer: Abdollah Jalilian <stat4aj@gmail.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Abdollah", "Jalilian", role = c("cre", "aut"),
    email = "stat4aj@gmail.com", comment=c(orcid = "0000-0002-6573-006"))
Description: This package simplifies access to environmental satellite data from 
    sources like the Copernicus Climate Data Store (see <https://cds.climate.copernicus.eu>), 
    Copernicus Atmosphere Data Store (see <https://ads.atmosphere.copernicus.eu/>), 
    and Microsoft Planetary Computer (see <https://planetarycomputer.microsoft.com/>). 
    Users must properly acknowledge all data sources by properly citing and 
    referencing datasets according to their licenses and terms of use. Development 
    of this package was supported by the Lancaster Ecology and Epidemiology Group (LEEG) 
    and funded by Biotechnology and Biological Sciences Research Council (BB/Y514238/1) 
    and the Wellcome Trust (220870/Z/20/Z).
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
